quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,104,"Say, \"O people, if you are in doubt concerning my religion, then [know that] I do not worship those whom you worship instead of God, but rather I worship God who will cause you to die, for I am commanded to be one of the believers"
  10,105,"And set your face towards the [true] faith in all uprightness, and do not be one of those who ascribe partners to God"
  10,106,"and do not invoke besides God what can neither help nor harm you. If you do, you will be one of the wrongdoers"
  10,107,"If God inflicts harm on you, no one can remove it but He, and if He intends good for you, no one can withhold His bounty; He grants His bounty to any of His servants whom He will. He is the Most Forgiving, and the Most Merciful"
  10,108,"Say, \"Mankind, Truth has come to you from your Lord! Anyone who accepts guidance is guided only for his own sake; and he who goes astray does so at his own peril. I am not appointed as your keeper"
  10,109,"Follow what is revealed to you, [O Prophet], and be steadfast until God gives His judgement. He is the Best of Judges"